ss=\"tg-baqh\">3/15</td>\n\n  </tr>\n\n  <tr>\n\n    <td class=\"tg-baqh\">AD</td>\n\n    <td class=\"tg-baqh\">$$<br>\\frac{4(E I)}{L}<br>$$</td>\n\n    <td class=\"tg-baqh\">4/15</td>\n\n  </tr>\n\n  <tr>\n\n    <td class=\"tg-c3ow\">AE</td>\n\n    <td class=\"tg-c3ow\">$$<br>\\frac{4(2 E I)}{L}<br>$$<br></td>\n\n    <td class=\"tg-c3ow\">8/15</td>\n\n  </tr>\n\n</tbody>\n\n</table>\n<p>$$ \\begin{aligned} &amp;(D F)_{A D\\left(\\text { when } I_{A D}=1\\right)}=\\frac{4}{15}=0.267\\\\ &amp;\\text { Assume flexural rigidity of number } \\mathrm{AD} \\text { is ' } 2 \\mathrm{EI} \\text { ' } \\end{aligned} $$</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://app-content.cdn.examgoal.net/fly/@width/image/jaoe38c1mbixvc6a/c702bd77-00b6-435c-a67a-d4f2932c4c1c/5934b420-41ce-11f0-b55b-2b590ab4dfce/file-jaoe38c1mbixvc6b.png?format=png\" data-orsrc=\"https://app-content.cdn.examgoal.net/image/jaoe38c1mbixvc6a/c702bd77-00b6-435c-a67a-d4f2932c4c1c/5934b420-41ce-11f0-b55b-2b590ab4dfce/file-jaoe38c1mbixvc6b.png\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"max-width:100%;height:auto;display:block;margin:0 auto;max-height:40vh;vertical-align:baseline\" alt=\"GATE CE 2025 Set 1 Structural Analysis - Moment Distribution Method Question 1 English Explanation 2\"></p>\n<style type=\"text/css\">\n\n.tg  {border-collapse:collapse;border-spacing:0;}\n\n.tg td{border-color:black;border-style:solid;border-width:1px;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;font-size:14px;\n\n  overflow:hidden;padding:10px 5px;word-break:normal;}\n\n.tg th{border-color:black;border-style:solid;border-width:1px;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;font-size:14px;\n\n  font-weight:normal;overflow:hidden;padding:10px 5px;word-break:normal;}\n\n.tg .tg-c3ow{border-color:inherit;text-align:center;vertical-align:top}\n\n</style>\n<table class=\"tg\"><thead>\n\n  <tr>\n\n    <th class=\"tg-c3ow\">Joint</th>\n\n    <th class=\"tg-c3ow\">member</th>\n\n    <th class=\"tg-c3ow\">stiffness</th>\n\n    <th class=\"tg-c3ow\">\\text { Total stiffness }</th>\n\n    <th class=\"tg-c3ow\">DF</th>\n\n  </tr></thead>\n\n<tbody>\n\n  <tr>\n\n    <td class=\"tg-c3ow\" rowspan=\"4\">A</td>\n\n    <td class=\"tg-c3ow\">AC</td>\n\n    <td class=\"tg-c3ow\">0</td>\n\n    <td class=\"tg-c3ow\" rowspan=\"4\">$$<br>\\frac{19 E I}{L}<br>$$<br></td>\n\n    <td class=\"tg-c3ow\">0</td>\n\n  </tr>\n\n  <tr>\n\n    <td class=\"tg-c3ow\">AB</td>\n\n    <td class=\"tg-c3ow\">$$<br>\\frac{3(E I)}{L}<br>$$<br></td>\n\n    <td class=\"tg-c3ow\">3/19</td>\n\n  </tr>\n\n  <tr>\n\n    <td class=\"tg-c3ow\">AD</td>\n\n    <td class=\"tg-c3ow\">$$<br>\\frac{2(\\mathrm{EI})}{\\mathrm{L}}<br>$$<br></td>\n\n    <td class=\"tg-c3ow\">8/19</td>\n\n  </tr>\n\n  <tr>\n\n    <td class=\"tg-c3ow\">AE</td>\n\n    <td class=\"tg-c3ow\">$$<br>\\frac{4(2 \\mathrm{EI})}{\\mathrm{L}}<br>$$<br></td>\n\n    <td class=\"tg-c3ow\">8/19</td>\n\n  </tr>\n\n</tbody>\n\n</table>\n<p>$$ \\begin{aligned} (D F)_{A D\\left(\\text { when } \\mathrm{I}_{\\mathrm{AD}}=2 n\\right.} &amp; =\\frac{8}{19}=0.421 \\\\ \\text {} \\quad \\mathrm{I}_{\\mathrm{AF}} &amp; =2 \\mathrm{I} \\text { and } \\mathrm{I}_{\\mathrm{FD}}=\\mathrm{I} . \\end{aligned} $$</p>\n<p>If,</p>\n<p> then $(D F)_{A D}$ should lies between $(0.267)$ and $(0.421)$ only option (b) lies in this range</p>\n<p>So,</p>\n<p>$$ (D F)_{A D \\text { for given frame }}=0.398 $$</p>",
